<plot>This made-for-DVD documentary details the work that went into the production of Roadgames, Richard Franklin's psychological thriller about a truck driver who suspects another motorist of murder, but who himself falls under suspicion when he tries to follow up his hunches. Mystery fans are treated to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of this homage to Hitchcock, as well as to interviews with star Stacey Keach, who gives his insights into the efforts that were needed to bring this project to completion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?285987</url></doc>
